Ongoing & proposed Projects by the Nigerian Government in the Power Sector in Collaboration with the African Development Bank Group. These projects across Nigerian include substation constructions and rehabilitation, reconductoring of transmission lines and construction of new ones. The Hon. Minister of Power, Engr. Sale Mamman expects these projects to be completed before the end of 2020 to help improve the delivery of Electricity across Nigeria. Tanimu is an Online Editor with Africa's Largest TV Network. Produces when not on Social media.